Welcome, dear lady.

126
00:06:35,832 --> 00:06:37,832
Yes, welcome.

127
00:06:46,832 --> 00:06:48,832
Miss Rottenmeier, come to yourself.

128
00:06:48,832 --> 00:06:50,832
What's wrong with her?

129
00:06:50,832 --> 00:06:52,832
