246
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:38,510
Mrs. Rottenmeier wishes that I draw your attention to the fact that we only eat
at 7 o'clock according to the house rules.

247
00:14:38,510 --> 00:14:42,510
What? Only at 7 o'clock? But then we have to wait another half hour.

248
